### Testing Steps

**1. Setup & Login**
```javascript
// Navigate to app
mcp_chrome-devtools_navigate_page({ url: "http://localhost:3000" })

// Take snapshot
mcp_chrome-devtools_take_snapshot({ verbose: false })

// Login
mcp_chrome-devtools_fill_form({
  elements: [
    { uid: "[email-input-uid]", value: "admin10@nynus.edu.vn" },
    { uid: "[password-input-uid]", value: "Abd8stbcs!" }
  ]
})
```

**2. Console Analysis** (Errors only)
```javascript
// Get errors and warnings
mcp_chrome-devtools_list_console_messages({
  types: ["error", "warn"],
  pageSize: 50
})

// Get detail
mcp_chrome-devtools_get_console_message({ msgid: [id] })
```

**3. Network Check**
```javascript
// List requests
mcp_chrome-devtools_list_network_requests({
  resourceTypes: ["fetch", "xhr"],
  pageSize: 50
})

// Check for: failed (4xx, 5xx), slow requests (>1s)
```

**4. UI/UX Inspection**
```javascript
// Take full screenshot
mcp_chrome-devtools_take_screenshot({
  fullPage: true,
  format: "png",
  filePath: "full-page.png"
})

// Test responsive
mcp_chrome-devtools_resize_page({ width: 375, height: 667 })  // Mobile
mcp_chrome-devtools_resize_page({ width: 1920, height: 1080 }) // Desktop
```

**5. Interaction Test**
- Forms submit correctly
- Validation errors show
- Success messages appear
- No dead-end states

**6. Performance** (Optional)
```javascript
mcp_chrome-devtools_performance_start_trace({
  reload: true,
  autoStop: true
})

// Check: LCP < 2.5s, FID < 100ms, CLS < 0.1
```

