## ✅ Testing Checklist

- [ ] All 3 roles tested (admin, teacher, student)
- [ ] Console: no critical errors
- [ ] Network: no failed requests
- [ ] UI: no visual issues (mobile/tablet/desktop)
- [ ] Forms: validation works, submission works
- [ ] Navigation: all links work
- [ ] Performance: acceptable (if checked)

