## 🚨 Critical Issues (Stop & Report)

- ❌ Authentication bypass or security vulnerability
- ❌ Data loss (user data not saved)
- ❌ Application crash on critical path
- ❌ gRPC connection failures
- ❌ Exposed sensitive data

